<m0>House approves measure retaining<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .13 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>health insurance after loss of job<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 2.16 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .986 INCHES<m2><ql>
